<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Document Review Update</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        color: #333333;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #2d3748;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 0.9em;
        color: #555555;
      }
      .status-box {
        background: #f0fff4;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border-radius: 5px;
        border-left: 4px solid #48bb78;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Document Review Update</h1>

    <p>Dear <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>

    <p>Thank you for submitting your application to MDMAT. We appreciate your interest in our services and look forward to assisting you.</p>

    <div class="status-box">
      <p>We have reviewed and <strong>approved</strong> your <%= format_proof_type(@proof_review.proof_type) %> documentation.</p>
      <% if @application.all_proofs_approved? %>
        <p>Great news! All your required documentation has been approved. We will now proceed with requesting certification from your healthcare provider.</p>
      <% end %>
    </div>

    <p>If you need assistance or have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us at <%= mail_to "info@mdmat.org" %>.</p>

    <p>Best regards,<br>The MDMAT Team</p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
